reviews.text: Great staff and service ,the station as a taxi rank just outside the main entrance too,all local taxi drivers with a great knowledge of the area.

If you're changing for the Barnes branch on a train coming from reading, change here rather than Staines or anywhere else. You get better chance of grabbing a seat, and if you smoke, you can step into the car park for a quick puff while waiting for your connection without going through any barriers. very useful.
Well it’s ok but it doesn’t have atm and the ticketing machine wasn’t working
Outside the oyster zone but still useful.

Unbelievable that there are no one star ratings. It needs one. Probably the ugliest station I've seen - but most stations on this line are ugly. The two little bridges look as if they should have been condemned years ago. Shocking
